Yek '''kher''' (vai '''khǎr''') si yek than kai beshen thai jipen le manusha, kerdo te garuvel len katar [[brishind]], [[balval]], [[tatipen]], [[shil]] vai biamala. Si les zidurya (pashavre), uchhardo thai yek vai buteder livnya (kherkotora, sobe, besharnya). Les si les yek vai buteder udara, pale varesave purane khera (sar kai [[Chatalhöyük]]) labyarden uchharde thai shopnya te den andre. Vi si les dikhavne (filyastre) te del andre o [[Kham]]esko dud thai te dikhel pes avri.

O lav si [[Indo-Aryano]] ([[Hindi]]: घर - ghǎr).

